iewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin mx-auto h-9 w-9 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-muted\">المدينة</h3><p class=\"mt-2 font-display text-lg font-black text-[#1D1916]\">الرياض</p></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-badge-check mx-auto h-9 w-9 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3.85 8.62a4 4 0 0 1 4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 6.74 0 4 4 0 0 1 4.78 4.78 4 4 0 0 1 0 6.74 4 4 0 0 1-4.77 4.78 4 4 0 0 1-6.75 0 4 4 0 0 1-4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 0-6.76Z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-muted\">حالة المساهمة</h3><p class=\"mt-2 font-display text-lg font-black text-[#1D1916]\">متاحة للاستثمار</p></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-banknote mx-auto h-9 w-9 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"12\" x=\"2\" y=\"6\" rx=\"2\"></rect><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"></circle><path d=\"M6 12h.01M18 12h.01\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-muted\">الحد الأدنى للاستثمار</h3><p class=\"mt-2 font-display text-lg font-black text-[#1D1916]\">50,000 ريال</p></article></div><div class=\"mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-3\"><a class=\"inline-flex h-12 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-[#A7815E] px-7 text-sm font-extrabold text-white\" href=\"/contributions\">الانتقال إلى جهة الطرح <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-external-link h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 3h6v6\"></path><path d=\"M10 14 21 3\"></path><path d=\"M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6\"></path></svg></a><button type=\"button\" class=\"inline-flex h-12 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-[#A7815E]/45 bg-white px-7 text-sm font-extrabold text-[#8F6B4C]\" aria-busy=\"false\" aria-pressed=\"false\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5\"></path></svg>الاهتمام بالمساهمة</button></div></div></div><section class=\"mt-8 grid items-center gap-6 rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 lg:grid-cols-[0.75fr_1.25fr]\"><div class=\"relative h-44 overflow-hidden rounded-md bg-surface\"><img alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-contain\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"35vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcontribution-request-hero-sketch.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcontribution-request-hero-sketch.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcontribution-request-hero-sketch.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcontribution-request-hero-sketch.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcontribution-request-hero-sketch.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcontribution-request-hero-sketch.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcontribution-request-hero-sketch.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcontribution-request-hero-sketch.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcontribution-request-hero-sketch.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcontribution-request-hero-sketch.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcontribution-request-hero-sketch.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"text-right\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">نبذة عن المساهمة</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm font-bold leading-9 text-muted\">مساهمة تطويرية منظمة لمجمع تجاري في الرياض وفق أعلى معايير الحوكمة والإفصاح.<!-- --> تهدف المساهمة إلى تطوير وتشغيل مجمع أعمال حديث في أحد المواقع الحيوية بمدينة الرياض، مع إدارة احترافية وتقارير دورية وحوكمة واضحة.</p></div></section><section class=\"mt-7\"><h2 class=\"mb-5 text-right font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">معلومات المساهمة</h2><div class=\"grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6\"><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-building2 lucide-building-2 mx-auto h-9 w-9 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 12h4\"></path><path d=\"M10 8h4\"></path><path d=\"M14 21v-3a2 2 0 0 0-4 0v3\"></path><path d=\"M6 10H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2\"></path><path d=\"M6 21V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v16\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-muted\">نوع المساهمة</h3><p class=