h.01\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-muted\">الحد الأدنى للاستثمار</h3><p class=\"mt-2 font-display text-lg font-black text-[#1D1916]\">50,000 ريال</p></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-building2 lucide-building-2 mx-auto h-9 w-9 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 12h4\"></path><path d=\"M10 8h4\"></path><path d=\"M14 21v-3a2 2 0 0 0-4 0v3\"></path><path d=\"M6 10H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2\"></path><path d=\"M6 21V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v16\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-muted\">الجهة الطارحة</h3><p class=\"mt-2 font-display text-lg font-black text-[#1D1916]\">شركة الطرح العقاري</p></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar mx-auto h-9 w-9 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-muted\">مدة الاستثمار</h3><p class=\"mt-2 font-display text-lg font-black text-[#1D1916]\">24 شهراً</p></article></div></section><section class=\"mt-7 grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5\"><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-right font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">موقع المشروع</h2><div class=\"grid gap-4 lg:grid-cols-[170px_1fr]\"><dl class=\"grid gap-3 text-sm font-bold text-muted\"><d