vg></div></div></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5\"><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-right font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">مؤشرات المشروع</h2><div class=\"grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3\"><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trending-up mx-auto h-9 w-9 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 7h6v6\"></path><path d=\"m22 7-8.5 8.5-5-5L2 17\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-muted\">فرصة استثمارية</h3><p class=\"mt-2 font-display text-lg font-black text-[#1D1916]\">8% - 10%</p></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check mx-auto h-9 w-9 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-muted\">مشروع منظم</h3><p class=\"mt-2 font-display text-lg font-black text-[#1D1916]\">طرح مرخص</p></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-file-search mx-auto h-9 w-9 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M6 22a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2.4 2.4 0 0 1 1.704.706l3.588 3.588A2.4 2.4 0 0 1 20 8v12a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z\"></path><path d=\"M14 2v5a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h5\"></path><circle cx=\"11.5\" cy=\"14.5\" r=\"2.5\"></circle><path d=\"M13.3 16.3 15 18\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-muted\">حوكمة وشفافية</h3><p class=\"mt-2 font-display text-lg font-black text-[#1D1916]\">تقارير دورية</p></article></div></div></section><section class=\"mt-7 grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-right\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">الجهة الطارحة</h2><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-building2 lucide-building-2 mt-5 h-20 w-20 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 12h4\"></path><path d=\"M10 8h4\"></path><path d=\"M14 21v-3a2 2 0 0 0-4 0v3\"></path><path d=\"M6 10H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2\"></path><path d=\"M6 21V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v16\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-3 font-display text-xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">شركة الطرح العقاري</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm font-bold leading-8 text-muted\">شركة متخصصة في إدارة وطرح المساهمات العقارية وفق الأنظمة والضوابط المعتمدة.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-right\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">الاستثمار متاح عبر الجهة المرخصة</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm font-bold leading-8 text-muted\">للاطلاع على شروط الاستثمار والتفاصيل الكاملة يرجى زيارة موقع الجهة الطارحة.</p><a class=\"mt-5 inline-flex h-12 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-[#A7815E] px-7 text-sm font-extrabold text-white\" href=\"/contributions\">الانتقال إلى جهة الطرح <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-external-link h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 3h6v6\"></path><path d=\"M10 14 21 3\"></path><path d=\"M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6\"></path></svg></a></div></section><section class=\"mt-7\"><h2 class=\"mb-5 text-right font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">خدمات مرتبطة بالمساهمة</h2><div class=\"grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6\"><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-4 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-square-text mx-auto h-8 w-8 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M22 17a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6.828a2 2 0 0 0-1.414.586l-2.202 2.202A.71.71 0 0 1 2 21.286V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z\"></path><path d=\"M7 11h10\"></path><path d=\"M7 15h6\"></path><path d=\"M7 7h8\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold leading-6 text-[#1D1916]\">استشارة عقارية أولية</h3></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-4 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-search-check mx-auto h-8 w-8 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m8 11 2 2 4-4\"></path><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"8\"></circle><path d=\"m21 21-4.3-4.3\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold leading-6 text-[#1D1916]\">استشارة عقارية مفصلة</h3></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-4 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-badge-check mx-auto h-8 w-8 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3.85 8.62a4 4 0 0 1 4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 6.74 0 4 4 0 0 1 4.78 4.78 4 4 0 0 1 0 6.74 4 4 0 0 1-4.77 4.78 4 4 0 0 1-6.75 0 4 4 0 0 1-4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 0-6.76Z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold leading-6 text-[#1D1916]\">تقييم عقاري</h3></article></div><div class=\"mt-5 text-center\"><a class=\"inline-flex h-11 items-center rounded-md border border-[#A7815E]/45 px-7 text-sm font-extrabold text-[#8F6B4C]\" href=\"/request-study\">طلب خدمة عقارية +</a></div></section><section class=\"mt-8\"><div class=\"mb-5 flex items-center justify-between gap-4\"><a class=\"inline-flex h-10 items-center rounded-md border border-line bg-white px-4 text-xs font-extrabold text-navy\" href=\"/contributions\">عرض جميع المساهمات</a><h2 class=\"font-display text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916] gold-divider\">مساهمات مشابهة</h2></div><div class=\"grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-4\"><article class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-line bg-white\"><div class=\"relative h-32 overflow-hidden bg-surface\"><img alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover grayscale-[8%] sepia-[8%]\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"25vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcontribution-request-hero-sketch.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcontribution-request-hero-sketch.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcontribution-request-hero-sketch.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcontribution-request-hero-sketch.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcontribution-request-hero-sketch.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcontribution-request-hero-sketch.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcontr